sentences: Nuntita Khampiranon (Thai: นันทิตา ฆัมภิรานนท์; RTGS: Nanthita Khamphiranon; born December 20, 1983), or nickname Art (อาร์ต), stage name Bell (เบลล์) and usually known as Bell Nuntita, is a Thai transgender actress, singer, entertainer, and radio DJ.
Nuntita was part of a TV show called Venus Flytrap Search for the Missing Puzzle in 2007.
However, today her family has accepted her and she is happy.
In an April episode of the show, the judges picked Nuntita to be one of 48 semi-finalists.
Bell was also featured on the front cover of Who Weekly Magazine.
In July 2011, she held a one-night concert for her fans in Singapore.
